Round ← (×⊃(¬\↥=1|\+)+1⌊×6⍥⚂20) # Roll 20 times and calculate scores (inc 0s).
P₁    ← (⊡1Round)               # Pick score after 2 rolls.
P₂    ← (⊡4Round)               # Pick score after 5 rolls. Better.
P₃    ← (⍣⊢0▽⊸≥20Round)         # 20 or bust. Best non-adaptive strategy.
∩₃/+⍥⊃(P₁|P₂|P₃)10000
